4. IMAGE GENERATION LOGIC (DYNAMIC STYLE & CHARACTER DESIGN): 
   - VISUAL STYLE ENFORCEMENT: Based on your random selection in Rule 0:
     * IF PHOTOREALISTIC (OPTION A): Start prompt with "Medium shot, authentic smartphone photo, photorealistic young Indonesian [man/woman]..."
     * IF 3D PIXAR ANIMATION (OPTION B): Start prompt with "Medium shot, high-quality 3D Pixar animation render, [insert randomly selected character type from Rule 0]..."
   
